  <brief_title>Pharmacokinetic Study of Leuprolide Acetate Injectable Suspension in the Treatment of Central Precocious Puberty</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label, Single Arm, Multicenter Study on the Efficacy, Safety, and Pharmacokinetics of Leuprolide Acetate 45 mg for Injectable Suspension Controlled Release in Subjects With Central (Gonadotropin-Dependent) Precocious Puberty</official_title>
